{"tid":2131827,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[LOL] 怕爆！韓國玩家打字「Free HK」…中國選手秒關遊戲","createTime":"2020-07-30T05:53:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T06:28:31.000Z","uid":58219,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"700672016049cc3cb0c5337d6c77c8e01d0da961","tid":2131827,"uid":58219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T05:53:25.000Z","msg":"2020/07/29 20:16:00<br />\n記者林柏廷／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n退役前效力於中國知名《英雄聯盟》隊伍RNG的打野選手劉世宇（比賽ID：Mlxg）日前在直播時遭到一名韓國玩家嘲諷，而Mlxg也隨即以「你媽死了」等頗具中國特色的羞辱詞語回嘴。然而，該名韓國玩家在對話框打出「Free Hong Kong」這句話時，Mlxg竟然慌了，急忙遮蔽對話框並強制關閉遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n前RNG戰隊打野選手Mlxg自退役後，便時常開啟實況與粉絲互動。其在昨（28）日深夜的對局中遭到一名韓國玩家嘲諷「走開，醜陋的中國人」。Mlxg隨即以「你媽死了」、「我是你爹」等言詞回嘴，就這樣在雙方的互罵中結束該場遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/07/29/2690657-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F07%2F29%2F2690657-XXL.jpg&h=9e40b856&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲前RNG打野選手MLXG遭到韓國玩家嘲諷。（圖／翻攝自微博）<br />\n<br />\n冤家路窄，Mlxg在下一場對局又遇見了嘲諷他的韓國玩家。沒想到該玩家直接在對話框中打出「Free Hong Kong」，讓Mlxg瞬間手足無措，除了將對話框移出直播畫面外，也迅速的將遊戲強制關閉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/07/29/2690662-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F07%2F29%2F2690662-XXL.jpg&h=bb29a388&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲一句「Free Hong Kong」，讓Mlxg急忙遮蔽聊天室並秒關遊戲。（圖／翻攝自微博）<br />\n<br />\n起初Mlxg與該名韓國玩家在遊戲中還有來有回的互罵，沒想到該名韓國玩家僅僅以一句「Free Hong Kong」，就讓在賽場上身經百戰的Mlxg慌了手腳，急忙將遊戲強制關閉，似乎是害怕受到「黨的關切」。玩家的神來一句讓Mlxg瞬間噤聲，引起《英雄聯盟》社群的熱烈討論。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsource: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=788085&amp;utm_source=setn.com&amp;utm_medium=viewall&amp;utm_campaign=viewallnews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D788085%26utm_source%3Dsetn.com%26utm_medium%3Dviewall%26utm_campaign%3Dviewallnews&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhNxiqP1mjC8IHxs%2BzMkXvdI%3D&h=f7cabeb9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D788085%26utm_source%3Dsetn.com%26utm_medium%3Dviewall%26utm_campaign%3Dviewallnews&h=ec098ffa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=788085&amp;utm_source=setn.com&amp;utm_medium=viewall&amp;utm_campaign=viewallnews</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=17532&amp;snA=665514&amp;tnum=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D17532%26snA%3D665514%26tnum%3D3&d=6fRpkjTAYTcnGOSNIV5vhNxiqP1mjC8IHxs%2BzMkXvdI%3D&h=0c5c3e80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=17532&amp;snA=665514&amp;tnum=3</a>"},{"pid":"ea957fb38f6490935dcd2c5b76a6ace776311467","tid":2131827,"uid":237271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:01:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"96931d6431880be5db6cf76155ed25e5af1349a2","tid":2131827,"uid":81652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:04:07.000Z","msg":"中離reproted<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9064b4869868fd16cc108af97d6d18787b635584","tid":2131827,"uid":223006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:09:26.000Z","msg":"學查拜仁話齋, 唔中意呀? Quit左佢囉!!"},{"pid":"e5c198103173bdb9276d17c6e686fb0bec3e12f2","tid":2131827,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:24:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff35e07b8453b323dbdeb50900a876f7f51bcfe7","tid":2131827,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:28:31.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"orange\"><del>NMSL</del></span></span>"}]}